org.swerverobotics.library.interfaces

Class II2cDeviceClient.ReadWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • II2cDeviceClient.ReadWindow
  • Enclosing interface:
    II2cDeviceClient

    public static class II2cDeviceClient.ReadWindow
extends java.lang.Object
    RegWindow is a utility class for managing the window of I2C register bytes that are read from our I2C device on every hardware cycle

    • Field Detail

      • cregReadMax

        public static final int cregReadMax
        enableI2cReadMode and enableI2cWriteMode both impose a maximum length on the size of data that can be read or written at one time. cregReadMax and cregWriteMax indicate those maximum sizes.
